Test Row-Level Security for the Dataset 

 REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
Log in to CRM Analytics as Bill.
Open the OppRoles opportunity.
Notice that Bill can’t see his manager Keith’s opportunities anymore. Now, he can see only his opportunity and his subordinate Tony’s opportunity.
Log out and now log in as Keith.

As expected, Keith can still see all opportunities.
